title: Afraid To Debate? Leftist Journalist Won’t Do Bill Maher’s Show With Milo Yiannopoulos
text:
Afraid To Debate? Leftist Journalist Won’t Do Bill Maher’s Show With Milo Yiannopoulos Published February 17, 2017 AP 
By Lawrence Meyers, LifeZette Journalist Jeremy Scahill has pulled out of an appearance on Friday night’s episode of “Real Time with Bill Maher” to protest the fact that conservative commentator and Breitbart senior editor Milo Yiannopoulos will also appear on the show.
